annual San Fernando Fiesta. About 1,000 people turned out at Recreation Park on 
Sunday for the conclusion of the four-day celebration. The fiesta crowd was 
entertained by Latino bands, dance groups, carnival games and rides. HYUNGWON 
KANG / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
