<P>
Television personality Monty Hall says he can't even go to the men's room 
without some wag uttering his familiar line. 
</P>
<P>
Hall says it is almost inevitable when he walks into a restroom and faces a 
lineup of stalls that someone will say: "Do you want door No. 1, door No. 2 or 
