<P>
Third-seeded Martin Jaite of Argentina defeated West Germany's Markus Zoecke 
7-5, 6-4 today in the first round of the Swiss Open tennis tournament. 
</P>
<P>
Jaite needed 90 minutes to oust the unseeded Zoecke in an error-laced match, 
although the outcome never seemed in doubt after the first set. 
</P>
<P>
